item.title: CVE-2022-4298|2024-08-03T01:34:50.063Z -- unknown -- wholesale%20market
item.description: The Wholesale Market WordPress plugin before 2.2.1 does not have authorisation check, as well as does not validate user input used to generate system path, allowing unauthenticated attackers to download arbitrary file from the server.
